fields.name: Almond Butter
fields.description: King Markatta's organic Almond butter has a round delicious taste from organic lightly roasted sweet almonds. Suitable for desserts, smoothies or on a spoon just as it is

fields.name: Avocado oil
fields.description: Healthwell Avocado Oil EKO is a healthy cooking oil that can be used both for cold dishes and as frying oil. Avocado oil is rich in unsaturated fatty acids and can withstand high temperatures without being destroyed. Try drizzling over a salad, use for dressing and marinade or as frying fat.

fields.name: MCT oil
fields.description: Pureness MCT oil 250 ml is a high-quality fractionated coconut oil with medium-chain fatty acids. The name MCT comes from Medium Chain Triglycerides. MCT is anti-inflammatory and antioxidant and MCT oil from coconut is popular in LCHF. Feel free to have a teaspoon in your coffee in the morning! Our MCT oil contains 60% caprylic acid (C8) and 40% capric acid (C10). It is tasteless, odorless and colorless and is therefore very useful in cooking. It can withstand heating, but is not recommended for frying.

fields.name: Coconut flour
fields.description: Are you looking for a healthy flour substitute to bake healthy baked goods? In this case, Coconut Flour is made for you! Coconut flour is made exclusively from organic, fat-reduced coconut that is dried and finely ground. This flour is gluten-free and rich in fibers.

fields.name: Almond flour
fields.description: Almond Flour can be a good alternative for anyone who, for one reason or another, either cannot eat wheat flour or simply prefers not to. Our Fat-reduced Amond Flour is a finely-ground flour with 80% fat reduction through cold-pressing.

fields.name: Sesame flour
fields.description: Sesame Flour has a mild and nutty aroma which adds a delicious taste to baked goods. The round and slightly sweet taste of the flour is perfect for biscuits, cakes, bread, pizza, etc. The flour is an excellent alternative to almond flour and is used in exactly the same way.

fields.name: Sukrin
fields.description: Sukrin is a natural sugar substitute with zero calories. Sukrin has no carbohydrates that are absorbed by the body, and is perfect for anyone looking to maintain a low-calorie diet and stable blood sugar levels. Sukrin allows everyone to enjoy sweet treats as part of their everyday diet, completely guilt-free!

fields.name: Sukrin:1
fields.description: Sukrin:1 the healthy and natural alternative to caster sugar, without calories! Ideal for baking but also delicious to combine with coffee/tea or as sweet finishing touch!

fields.name: Sukrin:gold
fields.description: Sukrin Gold is similar to brown sugar, but contains far fewer calories and carbohydrates. So you can enjoy sweet again without the need to feel guilty!

fields.name: Sukrin:icing
fields.description: Sukrin Icing is the 100% natural and zero-calorie alternative to powdered sugar without compromising the sweet taste.

fields.name: Sukrin +
fields.description: Sukrin+ is Sukrin that has been combined with stevia. This provides a complete natural sweetener with double the sweetness of sugar. Sukrin+ combines the sugar consistency of Sukrin with the sweetness of stevia.

fields.name: Sukrin Syrup - Caramel
fields.description: Sukrin Caramel Syrup is a fiber-rich syrup and a healthy substitute for sugar syrup and caramel. Sukrin Caramel Syrup is a sweet syrup which contains low sugar, high fibers and a great taste!

fields.name: Sukrin Syrup - Maple
fields.description: Sukrin Maple Syrup is the ideal syrup for everyone who is looking for a healthy alternative to regular syrup. Due to the fact that the Maple Syrup does not contain only a very small amount of sugars, it is a healthy substitute that is high in fiber and has got a sweet taste!

fields.name: Sukrin Syrup - Gold
fields.description: Sukrin Syrup Gold is reduced on calories and completely gluten-free. The low sugar content makes Syrup Gold very gentle on your blood sugar, and additionally, the syrup is tooth-friendly but got still a sweet taste.

fields.name: Baking Mix
fields.description: Our Baking Mix makes it easy to bake delicious cakes and desserts that are both gluten and sugar-free.

fields.name: Chia Bread
fields.description: Super Bread Mix with chia is easy and quick to prepare. Free from gluten and artificial colors and flavors. The structure of the bread is similar to rye bread.

fields.name: Fibre Bread
fields.description: Be surprised by the rich taste of the Bread Mix reduced in carbs from Sukrin. Made from various seeds and kernels that give the bread a delicious bite. The structure of the bread is similar to rye bread.

fields.name: Cake in a cup – Dark Chocolate
fields.description: Everything you ever thought about cake is about to change! Introducing the revolutionary Cake in a Cup, the sensational healthy treat ready in your favorite cup or mug in just two minutes!

fields.name: Protein Powder – Cookies & Cream
fields.description: Drink more cookies! That's basically what you get to do with the Cookies & Cream protein Powder - each scoop is filled with protein cookie crumbles and blends to perfection

fields.name: Protein Powder – Cinnamon Crunch
fields.description: We've transformed casein and whey protein isolates into impossibly delicious flavors that are distinctly Quest. Shake up Quest Protein Powder with 8oz of water for a decadent post-workout shake or use it as a #CookClean ingredient swap to transform a carb-heavy cheat into a protein-reach treat. Quest Protein Powder has an incredibly high protein-to-calories percentage because we don't add unnecessary ingredients. It's just amazing taste and excellent nutrition.

fields.name: Protein Powder – Chocolate Milkshake
fields.description: Enjoy indulgent chocolate taste and creamier protein shakes with the macros you need when you try Quest Chocolate Milkshake Protein Powder.

fields.name: Protein Powder – Multi Purpose Mix
fields.description: Just pure protein - we made it with 24g of protein per serving, but we let you get creative to add your favorite flavors to our most protein-packed powder available.

fields.name: Protein Powder – Peanut Butter
fields.description: So much protein it's nuts! And the taste of this delicious peanut butter protein powder will go scoop for scoop with anything you've had from a jar. The 84% P/Cal tells you just how serious this flavor is!

fields.name: Protein Powder – Salted Caramel
fields.description: A protein powder so delicious, you might just think it's your cheat day. Sweet caramel flavor with a pinch of salty overtones in every sip.

fields.name: Protein Powder – Vanilla Milkshake
fields.description: Anything but basic, this vanilla milkshake flavored protein powder is rich and creamy with the nutrition you need.

fields.name: Favourite Bar Mix – 12pcs
fields.description: NICKS Favorite mix of best-selling chocolate bars without added sugar, gluten-free (12 bars)

fields.name: Chocolate Mix – 12pcs
fields.description: NICKS Chocolate mix with selected nut-free chocolate bars without added sugar, gluten-free (12 bars)

fields.name: B-vitamin Complex
fields.description: Every single essential B vitamin compiled into a single, easy tablet, providing your complete recommended intake alongside a selection of additional nutrients. B vitamins are some of the most vital vitamins in your diet, supporting a whole range of bodily processes. This simple tablet supplement helps you get your daily dosage every day with zero hassle. Our B Vitamin Complex Tablets provide you with 100% (or more) of your recommended intake of every B vitamin, as well as biotin, inositol, PABA and choline, which are commonly grouped in with B vitamins more broadly.

fields.name: Calcium + Vitamin D3 + Vitamin K1
fields.description: 3 of the most popular bone health nutrients combined into a single capsule, at effective doses, in their most effective forms. Each capsule provides 200mg of calcium, 1000iu of vitamin D3 and 50mcg of vitamin K1. Optimal bone health is essential to anyone who trains regularly, particularly those who put their bodies under serious strain such as weightlifters, powerlifters and endurance athletes. These tablets provide 3 of the most important nutrients for promoting bone health to support your body throughout your training programme. Each ingredient in our Calcium + Vitamin D3 + Vitamin K1 Capsules is dosed at effective levels, using their most effective forms. For example, the calcium comes in the form of calcium citrate, a highly bioavailable form that’s ready for your body to absorb. Their combined effects contribute to normal muscle function, normal bones and teeth and normal blood clotting. *Contains Calcium which is needed for the maintenance of normal bones.

fields.name: Vitamin B12
fields.description: High strength vitamin B12 in a convenient tablet form, providing 40,000% of your reference intake in a single, potently dosed supplement. Our Vitamin B12 Tablets 1000mcg are a specific, high-strength form of vitamin B12, which promotes normal function of the immune system and contributes to the reduction of tiredness and fatigue. Our Vitamin B12 1000mcg Tablets provide an impressive 1000mcg of vitamin B12, and at a far lower price than competing products. Intense training can put your body under stress, and vitamin B12 contributes to maintaining normal function of the immune system, normal red blood cell formation, and normal energy-yielding metabolism.

fields.name: Vitamin C
fields.description: High strength vitamin C in a convenient, one-a-day tablet form, providing 1250% of your recommended intake. Vitamin C is one of the most important nutrients in your daily diet. Our Vitamin C Tablets 1000mg are a specific, high strength form of vitamin C, which promotes normal function of the immune system and contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Our Vitamin C Tablets provide an impressive 1000mg of vitamin C, and at a far lower price than competing products. Intense training can put your body under stress, and vitamin C contributes to maintaining normal function of the immune system.
